1
00:00:00,340 --> 00:00:01,770
(All people, incidents,
and backgrounds...)

2
00:00:01,770 --> 00:00:03,440
(in this drama are fictitious
and unrelated to reality.)

3
00:00:03,440 --> 00:00:05,240
(Also, children were filmed
under production guidelines.)

4
00:00:05,980 --> 00:00:09,250
(Adele)

5
00:00:09,310 --> 00:00:10,620
(Episode 13)

6
00:00:13,180 --> 00:00:15,520
(Choi Yu Na,
Head of New Business Task Force)

7
00:00:39,110 --> 00:00:41,080
Good morning, Director Kim.

8
00:00:42,310 --> 00:00:43,310
Sure.

9
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:20,050
Jin Ju. Baek Jin Ju!

10
00:01:25,120 --> 00:01:26,260
Baek Jin Ju.

11
00:01:29,360 --> 00:01:31,130
Isn't that the name of Dr. Baek's...

12
00:02:13,270 --> 00:02:14,370
Choi Yu Na.

13
00:02:15,240 --> 00:02:18,810
So that's the look you get
just from hearing my name.

14
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:23,250
I was worried you'd forgotten me,
but I'm glad you didn't.

15
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:25,450
This makes coming back worthwhile.

16
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:50,740
Does the name Baek Jin Ju
bother you?

17
00:02:51,340 --> 00:02:52,340
Excuse me?

18
00:02:52,610 --> 00:02:55,180
It's just that you seemed
very bothered by it a moment ago.

19
00:02:55,810 --> 00:02:57,680
So who exactly is Baek Jin Ju?

20
00:03:01,190 --> 00:03:03,190
She's just someone I used to know.

21
00:03:04,020 --> 00:03:05,420
Her name sounded familiar,

22
00:03:06,020 --> 00:03:08,060
so I just wanted to check.
That's all.

23
00:03:08,530 --> 00:03:09,530
Is that so?

24
00:03:19,200 --> 00:03:20,200
But...

25
00:03:21,670 --> 00:03:24,080
do you really have time
to analyze my expression?

26
00:03:24,280 --> 00:03:27,510
You were passed over
for president again.

27
00:03:30,850 --> 00:03:32,220
You've been the director...

28
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:34,790
of the jewelry division
for nearly ten years, right?

29
00:03:35,820 --> 00:03:38,820
Your division isn't doing
as well as it used to.

30
00:03:39,590 --> 00:03:43,390
Still, the chairman keeps you
in the same position.

31
00:03:44,400 --> 00:03:46,200
If your son is going
to take over the company,

32
00:03:46,300 --> 00:03:49,670
you should have
a bigger role yourself.

33
00:03:50,740 --> 00:03:54,070
I guess the chairman
doesn't trust you, Director Kim.

34
00:04:00,880 --> 00:04:01,980
Please approve my request.

35
00:04:03,180 --> 00:04:05,280
If you find
this business plan acceptable,

36
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:07,190
I'd like to be put in charge
of Temi Bio,

37
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:09,290
which you recently acquired.

38
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:12,760
If you put me in charge of Temi Bio,

39
00:04:14,190 --> 00:04:15,730
I'll handle the dirty work...

40
00:04:16,290 --> 00:04:17,800
like your wife does.

41
00:04:27,070 --> 00:04:28,470
Dirty work, you say?

42
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:33,950
I wonder what made you want
to go that far.

43
00:04:34,910 --> 00:04:35,980
Whatever the reason,

44
00:04:36,550 --> 00:04:39,750
I don't want to use you like that.

45
00:04:42,090 --> 00:04:44,920
You're still keeping me
at arm's length.

46
00:04:47,130 --> 00:04:49,930
It's for your own protection.

47
00:04:50,360 --> 00:04:51,930
Because you still don't trust me.

48
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:54,030
I trust no one.

49
00:04:55,300 --> 00:04:58,700
I keep you and my wife
at the same distance,

50
00:04:59,800 --> 00:05:00,840
so it's fair.

51
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:04,210
Stop getting ahead of yourself.
Just focus...

52
00:05:04,640 --> 00:05:06,780
on the jewelry division
in your current position.

53
00:05:41,650 --> 00:05:44,050
Still, you lucked out.

54
00:05:44,550 --> 00:05:48,750
You lack the division or the title
to help you in the succession race,

55
00:05:49,990 --> 00:05:52,790
but you now have me on your side.

56
00:05:53,460 --> 00:05:56,190
Once I marry Min Jun,
we'll be family.

57
00:05:57,860 --> 00:05:59,600
My father's shares...

58
00:05:59,760 --> 00:06:03,070
will give you a guaranteed block
of friendly support.

59
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:05,870
By the way,

60
00:06:06,400 --> 00:06:07,910
how did your father...

61
00:06:08,010 --> 00:06:10,370
acquire shares in the Adele Group?

62
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:14,180
Did he receive them as a bonus
when he sold Temi Bio?

63
00:06:16,550 --> 00:06:17,550
Sorry?

64
00:06:19,750 --> 00:06:23,650
And it couldn't have been easy
to persuade the chairman,

65
00:06:23,860 --> 00:06:25,920
so how did you get his blessing
for the marriage?

66
00:06:26,860 --> 00:06:29,730
You and my Min Jun have a history,

67
00:06:29,730 --> 00:06:31,430
so why does it seem so strained now?

68
00:06:31,500 --> 00:06:32,860
Can you explain...

69
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:34,200
why this marriage...

70
00:06:34,630 --> 00:06:37,070
was forced on him
and arranged like a business deal?

71
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:40,440
That...

72
00:06:44,810 --> 00:06:48,580
I'll explain that to you later
in due time.

73
00:06:49,380 --> 00:06:52,520
Today's an important day
when our families officially meet.

74
00:06:53,750 --> 00:06:55,950
How about we talk about that first?

75
00:06:59,060 --> 00:07:00,120
I don't know about that.

76
00:07:00,630 --> 00:07:03,560
If you struggle to answer
such simple questions,

77
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:07,600
I doubt you can truly be on my side,

78
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:08,800
let alone become family.

79
00:07:14,710 --> 00:07:16,640
Both the family meeting
and the wedding...

80
00:07:17,070 --> 00:07:18,810
were simply ordered by the chairman.

81
00:07:35,130 --> 00:07:37,360
She needs my dad's shares
more than anyone,

82
00:07:38,600 --> 00:07:41,430
and yet she can't even defy
Chairman Park's orders.

83
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:45,840
Whatever.

84
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:48,340
Just like you said,

85
00:07:49,470 --> 00:07:50,580
this marriage...

86
00:07:51,980 --> 00:07:53,950
is a business deal I struck
with Chairman Park.

87
00:08:00,120 --> 00:08:02,320
I see
you're openly recording me now.

88
00:08:03,860 --> 00:08:06,020
It's a habit.
A way of keeping records.

89
00:08:06,490 --> 00:08:07,490
So.

90
00:08:08,730 --> 00:08:11,460
You want to be Head of Brand...

91
00:08:11,530 --> 00:08:13,830
for the Adele Group,

92
00:08:14,200 --> 00:08:17,070
overseeing the brands
of all our subsidiaries.

93
00:08:18,540 --> 00:08:21,670
I also studied marketing
while I was abroad.

94
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:24,280
After I marry Min Jun...

95
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:26,940
and we take over Adele Group,

96
00:08:28,080 --> 00:08:30,510
I figured I'd have to manage
the various subsidiaries, too.

97
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:45,130
Marriage followed by succession?

98
00:08:47,530 --> 00:08:48,930
That's rather arrogant,
wouldn't you say?

99
00:08:51,400 --> 00:08:52,400
Temi Bio.

100
00:08:55,170 --> 00:08:56,540
Looking back,

101
00:08:57,610 --> 00:09:01,850
you must regret giving my father
all those Adele Group shares.

102
00:09:03,480 --> 00:09:05,450
If I marry Min Jun,

103
00:09:06,720 --> 00:09:09,290
those shares will belong to him.

104
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:12,920
Without you having to carve out
a piece of your own shares,

105
00:09:14,090 --> 00:09:16,590
you'll be able to solidify
Park Min Jun's position.

106
00:09:19,730 --> 00:09:20,970
From your time abroad,

107
00:09:22,700 --> 00:09:24,400
it looks like
you brought back more...

108
00:09:25,400 --> 00:09:26,540
than just a diploma.

109
00:09:28,410 --> 00:09:30,310
That's because
I've decided to think...

110
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:32,740
and make decisions just like you.

111
00:09:35,210 --> 00:09:36,280
The person I am now...

112
00:09:37,320 --> 00:09:38,720
is far more useful...

113
00:09:39,680 --> 00:09:41,550
than I was back then.

114
00:09:44,590 --> 00:09:48,060
Still, the Head of Brand position
would be asking for too much.

115
00:09:49,290 --> 00:09:51,960
Head of the New Business Task Force.

116
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:57,440
Start there and prove your worth.

117
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:01,340
It's a smaller role
than I had in mind,

118
00:10:02,570 --> 00:10:03,840
but I'll take it...

119
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,940
on one condition.

120
00:10:06,480 --> 00:10:08,850
Have the wedding
take place immediately.

121
00:10:22,960 --> 00:10:25,030
Now that Chairman Park
has given his approval,

122
00:10:27,160 --> 00:10:28,830
no one can get in my way.

123
00:10:32,740 --> 00:10:33,870
Park Min Jun.

124
00:10:35,610 --> 00:10:36,840
(Head of Division 1 Park Min Jun)

125
00:10:40,410 --> 00:10:43,010
This is what he did with the gifts
for my parents?

126
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:53,320
See? This is why you drink
at the office.

127
00:10:54,190 --> 00:10:56,630
The simple pleasure of day drinking.

128
00:10:57,330 --> 00:10:58,530
This is fantastic.

129
00:11:02,530 --> 00:11:05,240
Just skip the family meeting. Okay?

130
00:11:06,270 --> 00:11:09,970
Call off this wedding
you don't even want. Darn it.

131
00:11:11,140 --> 00:11:14,180
You should finally tell your mom
about Baek Jin Ju.

132
00:11:14,650 --> 00:11:16,750
She thinks
you stopped talking to her...

133
00:11:16,750 --> 00:11:18,820
because she kept you
from going abroad.

134
00:11:18,920 --> 00:11:22,320
And she has this crazy idea
that your girlfriend was Choi Yu Na.

135
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,660
It's too much trouble.

136
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:28,560
It's not like telling her
will change anything.

137
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:30,290
Are you still holding a grudge?

138
00:11:31,630 --> 00:11:34,430
You fought with Baek Jin Ju
over your plans to study abroad,

139
00:11:36,570 --> 00:11:38,470
and she died
before you could apologize.

140
00:11:39,100 --> 00:11:40,740
You still think
that's all your mom's fault?

141
00:11:42,970 --> 00:11:45,040
Don't tell me you're still thinking
about Baek Jin Ju.

142
00:11:49,850 --> 00:11:51,650
All you ever talk about
is Baek Jin Ju.

143
00:11:51,950 --> 00:11:53,650
When will this end?

144
00:11:54,150 --> 00:11:56,150
Do you think this is the time
to be like this?

145
00:11:56,850 --> 00:11:58,160
At this rate,

146
00:12:01,730 --> 00:12:03,990
you could lose your position
as the heir.

147
00:12:07,470 --> 00:12:09,700
Stop being a fool and face reality.

148
00:12:10,500 --> 00:12:11,540
I'm...

149
00:12:12,440 --> 00:12:15,070
the one you need,
not the ghost of Baek Jin Ju.

150
00:12:16,070 --> 00:12:18,440
You know that. That's why
you agreed to this marriage.

151
00:12:19,940 --> 00:12:21,980
If you're going to do this,
then do it right.

152
00:12:25,350 --> 00:12:27,690
Didn't you agree to this
knowing exactly what it involved?

153
00:12:29,250 --> 00:12:30,250
What?

154
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:34,190
This marriage is just
an annoying chore for me.

155
00:12:34,730 --> 00:12:36,760
It's a hassle
to go against my father,

156
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,960
and since it can't be Jin Ju,

157
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:40,160
I'm getting it over with
no matter who it's with.

158
00:12:41,970 --> 00:12:43,830
Even knowing all that,

159
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:46,540
you expect me to pretend
we're happy and in love?

160
00:12:48,310 --> 00:12:50,440
Isn't that being greedy?

161
00:12:53,110 --> 00:12:56,210
You stole her designs
and her dreams,

162
00:12:56,280 --> 00:12:58,380
and now
you're stealing her marriage.

163
00:13:00,050 --> 00:13:01,750
So leave it at that.

164
00:13:02,250 --> 00:13:04,260
Don't get greedy
and think you can have me too.

165
00:13:12,130 --> 00:13:14,930
Baek Jin Ju wins again, as always.

166
00:13:17,230 --> 00:13:21,070
You've relentlessly thrown yourself
at him for years,

167
00:13:21,140 --> 00:13:22,540
but he still hasn't warmed up
to you.

168
00:13:23,510 --> 00:13:25,380
The Baek Jin Ju effect...

169
00:13:26,340 --> 00:13:27,580
is really something else.

170
00:13:33,380 --> 00:13:36,720
Baek Jin Ju!

171
00:13:38,420 --> 00:13:40,060
I knew today was off to a bad start.

172
00:13:42,460 --> 00:13:43,530
Just why?

173
00:13:45,500 --> 00:13:47,700
She's dead,
so why won't she stay that way?

174
00:13:48,570 --> 00:13:50,500
Why?

175
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,810
(Choi Yu Na)

176
00:14:03,810 --> 00:14:05,480
(Thank you for your reservation.
Enjoy your meal.)

177
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,260
Kim Myung Hui was passed over
for the promotion again?

178
00:14:17,130 --> 00:14:20,130
I'll give the board this.
They got this one right.

179
00:14:20,900 --> 00:14:21,900
Good.

180
00:14:22,330 --> 00:14:25,140
Let's hope they do even better
going forward.

181
00:14:25,670 --> 00:14:26,670
All right.

182
00:14:31,780 --> 00:14:33,410
My back's killing me.

183
00:14:34,110 --> 00:14:35,310
Did you get some good news?

184
00:14:36,110 --> 00:14:38,950
Kim Myung Hui got screwed again.

185
00:14:38,950 --> 00:14:39,980
Get the car.

186
00:14:40,450 --> 00:14:42,250
I just finished washing it.

187
00:14:42,250 --> 00:14:44,050
Can't I take a short break?

188
00:14:44,660 --> 00:14:46,790
You can rest on the way.

189
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:51,400
I rarely get to see
Kim Myung Hui look so miserable.

190
00:14:52,300 --> 00:14:55,170
Do you know how long I've waited
for this promotion cycle?

191
00:14:55,770 --> 00:14:58,500
I'm just going to change my clothes.
Have the car ready out front.

192
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:05,110
Mrs. Ok!

193
00:15:05,110 --> 00:15:06,140
Yes, ma'am.

194
00:15:07,280 --> 00:15:10,710
Have one of my favorite wines
ready tonight.

195
00:15:10,880 --> 00:15:13,180
I want to savor it
right in front of Kim Myung Hui.

196
00:15:13,950 --> 00:15:16,190
I'm afraid that won't be possible.

197
00:15:16,620 --> 00:15:18,490
Ms. Kim is having dinner...

198
00:15:18,760 --> 00:15:20,360
with her future in-laws today.

199
00:15:22,160 --> 00:15:23,430
That's today?

200
00:15:24,600 --> 00:15:26,830
Of all the days, why tonight?

201
00:15:28,430 --> 00:15:31,470
Whatever.
I can't let this ruin my good mood.

202
00:15:31,970 --> 00:15:34,370
I'll go rub it in her face
twice as hard.

203
00:15:50,190 --> 00:15:52,560
I heard they passed you over
for the promotion again.

204
00:15:54,990 --> 00:15:57,860
The jewelry division
is losing power,

205
00:15:57,860 --> 00:15:59,930
and you're stuck there.

206
00:16:01,070 --> 00:16:02,600
That means the chairman...

207
00:16:03,400 --> 00:16:05,900
has decided Hyun Jun
will be his successor.

208
00:16:08,310 --> 00:16:10,810
You're smiling? You little...

209
00:16:14,580 --> 00:16:15,650
Hey!

210
00:16:19,880 --> 00:16:23,050
Am I the only one
who hasn't moved up?

211
00:16:24,190 --> 00:16:26,790
You haven't gotten anything
beyond that gallery yourself.

212
00:16:27,890 --> 00:16:30,030
Doesn't that make us even?

213
00:16:36,330 --> 00:16:37,770
Regardless,

214
00:16:38,640 --> 00:16:41,540
it means he didn't tip the scales
in your favor.

215
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:42,910
That means Hyun Jun has...

216
00:16:42,910 --> 00:16:44,910
a much bigger advantage
as the legitimate son.

217
00:16:45,140 --> 00:16:46,880
You think the board
and shareholders...

218
00:16:46,880 --> 00:16:49,610
would let a mistress's son
take over?

219
00:16:50,550 --> 00:16:52,350
We're going to win this anyway,

220
00:16:52,350 --> 00:16:55,320
so save your breath and get out.
Got it?

221
00:16:59,320 --> 00:17:00,320
Darn.

222
00:17:06,000 --> 00:17:07,000
Unbelievable.

223
00:17:09,570 --> 00:17:11,800
How can she not change at all?

224
00:17:12,770 --> 00:17:15,370
That's what makes her so terrifying.

225
00:17:16,170 --> 00:17:17,640
You think she's terrifying?

226
00:17:17,740 --> 00:17:19,110
She never hesitates...

227
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,810
or wavers. She's relentless.

228
00:17:21,880 --> 00:17:23,480
(Jewelry Division,
Director Kim Myung Hui)

229
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:25,750
She's committed a murder before,
and it didn't faze her.

230
00:17:26,820 --> 00:17:29,320
Every time I see Oh Jung Ran,
it hits me.

231
00:17:30,290 --> 00:17:34,190
That I'm up against someone
so terrifying and ruthless.

232
00:17:36,790 --> 00:17:40,500
I have to take Adele Group away
from that monster,

233
00:17:42,000 --> 00:17:45,240
but I'm still nothing more
than Chairman Park's mistress.

234
00:17:46,570 --> 00:17:49,140
I don't have a business, a title,

235
00:17:49,440 --> 00:17:50,840
or anyone on my side backing me up.

236
00:17:52,780 --> 00:17:54,380
That's why, under the pretext
of the succession war,

237
00:17:55,110 --> 00:17:57,350
I can't even object
to Min Jun's marriage.

238
00:17:58,920 --> 00:18:02,420
But Min Jun and Yu Na
go way back, don't they?

239
00:18:03,190 --> 00:18:05,920
It's not ideal
that she's Choi Sam Sik's daughter,

240
00:18:06,360 --> 00:18:07,860
but they were so close...

241
00:18:07,860 --> 00:18:09,390
that they once planned
to study abroad together.

242
00:18:10,190 --> 00:18:11,760
If it has to be
an arranged marriage,

243
00:18:11,760 --> 00:18:14,100
isn't she better than a stranger?

244
00:18:16,570 --> 00:18:18,600
I don't think
becoming a monster is a bad thing.

245
00:18:19,000 --> 00:18:20,970
You have to be a monster
so people...

246
00:18:21,510 --> 00:18:23,840
don't take what's yours
and walk all over you.

247
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:25,680
Instead of being crushed
and losing everything,

248
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,710
only to regret it later,

249
00:18:27,850 --> 00:18:30,510
I'd rather be ready
to become a monster.

250
00:18:32,220 --> 00:18:33,380
I wonder if Min Jun...

251
00:18:34,080 --> 00:18:36,190
really did have feelings for her.

252
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:42,890
I was relieved when I heard
they'd grown apart,

253
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:46,930
and now I'm wondering
if I should stop this marriage.

254
00:18:48,170 --> 00:18:50,930
This might be too much for Min Jun.

255
00:18:51,240 --> 00:18:52,240
It worries me.

256
00:18:52,540 --> 00:18:55,540
That's why you've prepared
a trump card to turn things around.

257
00:18:55,770 --> 00:18:57,070
If it all works out,

258
00:18:57,310 --> 00:18:59,380
we can play that card
however we want.

259
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:17,330
Hey.

260
00:19:20,660 --> 00:19:21,670
You.

261
00:19:23,000 --> 00:19:25,040
Why are you acting
so high and mighty?

262
00:19:25,570 --> 00:19:27,470
Was that supposed to be a greeting?

263
00:19:29,070 --> 00:19:32,880
You have no manners,
just like your mother.

264
00:19:35,080 --> 00:19:38,920
Then again, what could you learn
from a mistress for a mother?

265
00:19:40,080 --> 00:19:42,090
Not here. We're at the office.

266
00:19:42,090 --> 00:19:43,520
So what if we are at the office?

267
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:47,520
Are you embarrassed
that your mother's a mistress?

268
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:51,600
No. I'm afraid
this will embarrass Hyun Jun.

269
00:19:52,400 --> 00:19:53,930
Why would he be embarrassed?

270
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:58,000
Because you're shouting, Mom.

271
00:19:59,240 --> 00:20:01,200
How do you expect me not to shout?

272
00:20:01,640 --> 00:20:03,310
Did you hear that tone?

273
00:20:03,310 --> 00:20:05,610
He's being blatantly disrespectful.

274
00:20:05,680 --> 00:20:07,880
Come on, you started it.

275
00:20:07,880 --> 00:20:10,950
You can't play the victim
after throwing the first punch.

276
00:20:11,380 --> 00:20:13,020
I think you've said enough.

277
00:20:13,120 --> 00:20:14,950
Where's Mr. Song?
In the parking lot?

278
00:20:15,020 --> 00:20:17,190
- Come on.
- Hey! Let go.

279
00:20:17,320 --> 00:20:19,520
Wait. Gosh, my back.

280
00:20:20,020 --> 00:20:21,290
You think you're a big deal,

281
00:20:21,290 --> 00:20:24,130
just because you're getting married
and owning stock.

282
00:20:24,260 --> 00:20:26,030
- Get over yourself.
- Let's go.

283
00:20:26,100 --> 00:20:28,030
Stop acting so high and mighty.

284
00:20:28,130 --> 00:20:29,970
No matter how proud you act,

285
00:20:30,030 --> 00:20:31,670
you'll always be
the illegitimate son.

286
00:20:31,670 --> 00:20:35,510
The real disgrace isn't Hyun Jun.
It's you!

287
00:20:35,570 --> 00:20:39,010
Hold on a second. Not so fast.

288
00:20:41,080 --> 00:20:42,310
Darn.

289
00:20:43,610 --> 00:20:44,620
All right.

290
00:20:44,780 --> 00:20:49,090
Where on earth did you find
something like that?

291
00:20:50,520 --> 00:20:54,020
This, my dear, is straight
from the UK.

292
00:20:55,690 --> 00:20:59,400
I call it the British royal look.

293
00:21:00,160 --> 00:21:02,100
If we're dealing
with a mega-rich family,

294
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:04,030
we should go with a royal approach.

295
00:21:05,240 --> 00:21:08,510
Royalty?
More like a royal disappointment.

296
00:21:09,570 --> 00:21:10,570
What was that?

297
00:21:10,840 --> 00:21:14,210
Your mouth is certainly
running wild today.

298
00:21:14,810 --> 00:21:16,680
It's not that.

299
00:21:17,010 --> 00:21:20,280
I'm just worried about
what Yu Na will think.

300
00:21:21,250 --> 00:21:22,850
Is Yu Na anything like you?

301
00:21:23,390 --> 00:21:25,460
She got
her artistic sensibilities...

302
00:21:25,860 --> 00:21:28,190
from me truly.

303
00:21:29,060 --> 00:21:30,630
Just you wait and see.

304
00:21:30,890 --> 00:21:33,700
Yu Na is going to say her mom
looks absolutely stunning.

305
00:21:35,900 --> 00:21:36,930
Oh my, just gorgeous.

306
00:21:37,600 --> 00:21:38,600
Let's go.

307
00:21:40,840 --> 00:21:42,070
Then again,

308
00:21:42,910 --> 00:21:45,680
I wonder if becoming their in-laws
is really a good idea.

309
00:21:46,940 --> 00:21:48,980
The more I see Chairman Park,

310
00:21:49,680 --> 00:21:51,280
the more I realize
how extreme his greed is.

311
00:21:52,220 --> 00:21:55,750
What does he expect to gain from us
through this marriage?

312
00:22:22,680 --> 00:22:23,680
Come in.

313
00:22:32,360 --> 00:22:33,390
The prenuptial agreement, sir.

314
00:22:34,730 --> 00:22:37,530
It includes a clause stating
that if a divorce occurs,

315
00:22:37,730 --> 00:22:40,200
Choi Sam Sik will forfeit
all his Adele Group shares.

316
00:22:41,130 --> 00:22:43,670
Good. Keep it safe...

317
00:22:44,400 --> 00:22:47,300
and get her to sign it
right before the wedding.

318
00:22:47,700 --> 00:22:50,210
She won't want to cancel
when it's this close,

319
00:22:50,570 --> 00:22:52,640
so she'll sign it without a fuss.

320
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:58,250
As for the divorce,
we can arrange it...

321
00:22:58,950 --> 00:23:00,450
once we've milked them
for everything.

322
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:03,290
What if they refuse to get divorced?

323
00:23:06,190 --> 00:23:07,360
Then,

324
00:23:08,690 --> 00:23:13,400
I could make it look like
Choi Sam Sik and Choi Yu Na...

325
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:16,900
murdered Baek Jun Gi
and Baek Jin Ju.

326
00:23:18,070 --> 00:23:19,640
I'll have to remind them of that.

327
00:23:27,910 --> 00:23:29,350
Just perfect.

328
00:23:32,850 --> 00:23:34,890
All right, then.

329
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:37,520
Shall we go play along
with their little game?

330
00:23:39,660 --> 00:23:40,660
Let's go.

331
00:23:41,930 --> 00:23:43,890
- Goodness.
- Watch your step.

332
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:46,300
You need to start thinking
about your age.

333
00:23:46,700 --> 00:23:49,270
You'll end up bedridden
if you keep getting so worked up.

334
00:23:49,530 --> 00:23:51,470
Stop it. You're always nagging.

335
00:23:52,840 --> 00:23:54,500
Wait. Be careful.

336
00:24:04,410 --> 00:24:06,480
What's going on?
Where are you going all dressed up?

337
00:24:07,520 --> 00:24:10,420
Don't tell me you're meeting
Min Jun's future in-laws.

338
00:24:13,620 --> 00:24:15,590
What business do you have
going there?

339
00:24:16,090 --> 00:24:19,060
Why bother when
it's your mistress's son's wedding?

340
00:24:20,560 --> 00:24:21,670
Should I just not go?

341
00:24:23,300 --> 00:24:25,100
- Really?
- Only if I don't have to meet...

342
00:24:25,100 --> 00:24:26,470
Hyun Jun's future in-laws too.

343
00:24:26,670 --> 00:24:27,840
That's only fair.

344
00:24:28,570 --> 00:24:31,580
- Honey.
- What should I do, then?

345
00:24:32,810 --> 00:24:35,780
Why even ask?
You'll just do what you want anyway.

346
00:24:50,190 --> 00:24:54,530
This family has a wedding coming up,
yet no one is smiling.

347
00:24:55,470 --> 00:24:57,430
I don't understand
why they're forcing this marriage.

348
00:25:01,240 --> 00:25:03,510
This can't happen
when it's Hyun Jun's time to marry.

349
00:25:04,940 --> 00:25:05,940
No way.

350
00:25:07,510 --> 00:25:09,350
Come on.

351
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:14,120
Seriously.

352
00:25:15,990 --> 00:25:18,490
I knew I'd find you
moping around like this.

353
00:25:19,760 --> 00:25:23,390
Hey, if you're leaving,
grab that stuff and go.

354
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,000
If you're not,

355
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:27,700
then treat your brother here,

356
00:25:28,770 --> 00:25:29,930
and let's go get a drink.

357
00:25:42,850 --> 00:25:43,850
What brings you here?

358
00:25:44,920 --> 00:25:47,380
What? Am I somewhere I shouldn't be?

359
00:25:48,890 --> 00:25:50,090
That's not what I meant.

360
00:25:51,350 --> 00:25:54,660
I thought we could go together
to meet Min Jun's future in-laws.

361
00:25:55,790 --> 00:25:57,030
To meet the family?

362
00:25:57,390 --> 00:25:59,330
He's the eldest son
of the Adele family.

363
00:25:59,860 --> 00:26:02,400
I should be there in person,
no matter how busy I am.

364
00:26:03,130 --> 00:26:04,970
Let's leave before we hit traffic.

365
00:26:05,740 --> 00:26:07,600
Sure. I'll get ready immediately.

366
00:26:08,910 --> 00:26:09,910
Just a moment.

367
00:26:12,140 --> 00:26:13,410
There's an urgent work matter.

368
00:26:13,710 --> 00:26:15,150
I just need to send a quick message.

369
00:26:29,760 --> 00:26:32,200
Chairman Park is coming with me
to meet Min Jun's future in-laws.

370
00:26:32,860 --> 00:26:35,530
Please make sure Min Jun
doesn't try to get out of it.

371
00:26:36,170 --> 00:26:37,830
I'll buy as much time as I can.

372
00:26:42,610 --> 00:26:44,570
You see, Director Kim...

373
00:26:45,110 --> 00:26:46,580
asked me to bring...

374
00:26:47,380 --> 00:26:49,250
these gifts.

375
00:26:50,450 --> 00:26:52,180
She asked you to do it personally?

376
00:26:52,980 --> 00:26:57,650
Yes, she said she'll be traveling
with the chairman...

377
00:26:58,390 --> 00:27:00,560
and asked me to let you know.

378
00:27:05,160 --> 00:27:06,160
Okay, then.

379
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:16,940
Your mom's a master strategist.
I'll give her that.

380
00:27:17,540 --> 00:27:20,240
She's letting you know
Chairman Park is watching you,

381
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:22,080
so don't even think
about running away.

382
00:27:22,510 --> 00:27:24,050
That's her way of putting
the pressure on.

383
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:29,890
If you're not calling it off,
shouldn't you hurry?

384
00:27:41,160 --> 00:27:43,330
This hits a little too close
to home.

385
00:27:45,170 --> 00:27:48,070
Once they sell off Park Min Jun,
I'll be next.

386
00:27:49,110 --> 00:27:53,810
So do I get sold off,
or do I make a run for it?

387
00:27:54,810 --> 00:27:58,210
That's the big question.

388
00:28:01,550 --> 00:28:02,650
Min Jun...

389
00:28:05,760 --> 00:28:06,820
I wonder if he'll be okay.

390
00:28:17,630 --> 00:28:19,370
I told them to make it identical.

391
00:28:20,200 --> 00:28:21,240
It'll pass, right?

392
00:28:25,080 --> 00:28:26,080
Yes.

393
00:28:28,610 --> 00:28:30,210
It's a perfect replica.

394
00:28:30,680 --> 00:28:33,980
Good. I've already set up everything
for the next step.

395
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:36,990
From now on, everything will go
according to plan.

396
00:28:38,090 --> 00:28:39,590
Yes. I'm counting on you.

397
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:41,060
Of course.

398
00:28:58,170 --> 00:28:59,240
When I wear these clothes...

399
00:29:00,580 --> 00:29:01,740
and become Baek Jin Ju,

400
00:29:04,450 --> 00:29:06,750
I wonder
what expression you'll have.

401
00:29:10,720 --> 00:29:11,750
When I see that look on your face,

402
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:15,330
will I be able to handle it?

403
00:29:37,080 --> 00:29:39,350
- Wait, the sign!
- The sign!

404
00:29:41,550 --> 00:29:43,590
Nice reflexes.

405
00:29:43,590 --> 00:29:46,190
Well, that's nothing special.

406
00:29:51,660 --> 00:29:53,660
She looked familiar.

407
00:29:54,430 --> 00:29:56,630
Isn't she an assistant
to one of Adele's executives?

408
00:30:04,940 --> 00:30:06,580
What's with his style?

409
00:30:07,280 --> 00:30:09,080
He looks like a clown
in those white pants.

410
00:30:19,120 --> 00:30:20,120
Excuse me.

411
00:31:54,020 --> 00:31:56,920
(Pearl in Red)

412
00:31:57,020 --> 00:31:58,290
What happened to you?

413
00:31:58,290 --> 00:31:59,490
You weren't picking up,

414
00:31:59,490 --> 00:32:01,020
and you're not even going
to explain yourself?

415
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:03,090
You clearly have no idea,

416
00:32:03,090 --> 00:32:05,500
but you'll regret
underestimating Chairman Park.

417
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:07,400
He's an extremely dangerous man.

418
00:32:07,400 --> 00:32:08,870
You want the bio division...

419
00:32:09,000 --> 00:32:10,570
and to postpone the wedding?

420
00:32:10,970 --> 00:32:12,200
What is this nonsense?

421
00:32:12,200 --> 00:32:13,840
If we recruit Chloe,

422
00:32:14,340 --> 00:32:17,310
we'll get global attention
right from the start,

423
00:32:17,610 --> 00:32:21,410
and it'll be our best shot
at saving the bio division.

424
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:24,080
(Subtitles are provided by KOCOWA.)
